{"tid":104912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"口吃病患者請進","createTime":"2017-02-02T13:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T15:24:46.000Z","uid":79502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa26dbdf5864c14608e84d3a71c76e1d77449b4a","tid":104912,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"我有口吃，成18歲人 ，我想醫好佢，但又冇錢，屋企人唔知，我收得好埋，平時好少講野 ， 我個病徵好奇怪 ，平時自己一個人講野冇事，同外界，朋友講野有時就會發作，主要係講唔到隻字，同埋重複aaa，反而我試過上堂講野就好順口，唔知係咪有稿關係，讀報紙完全perfect池 😊<br />\n<br />\n諗到出黎社會果陣就心煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一定會有好多困難 ，因為我知我係fit既，醒目仔，但有時就係呢樣野kick住我，最後冇膽去完成件事 ， 到依家，我發覺變得越黎越廢，比身邊同年紀朋友進度慢一拍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打呢篇野主要睇下有冇人都有咁既問題，同睇下有冇人俾到意見 同改變方法  , thx"},{"pid":"f2af89e72d945b7110214272fb1284869ad57c2a","tid":104912,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"漏口就漏口啦"},{"pid":"db6a8c9400dfd09b5bb96d8ab835e2e7952d6d47","tid":104912,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"扮出來"},{"pid":"271d9d69106092c2a391b5c765f068c0e409159d","tid":104912,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"一氣呵成地呀～～～～睇下"},{"pid":"df4dcc16899d03dded02baaa70d4637d358f01d2","tid":104912,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"三個字 三個字 咁講"},{"pid":"fe160b6b5e01bf532ede17a275b229444e84de77","tid":104912,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:06:49.000Z","msg":"叫人激嬲你 你聽到眼火爆果陣就屌鳩佢<br />\n最好鬧人果陣要夾雜啲粗口同英文<br />\n然後講野就會好流利"},{"pid":"68bf45636e6ce38f79f42418f816fdea78500cff","tid":104912,"uid":54015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"社交恐懼症？<br />\n會唔會覺得其他人注意你就好緊張？<br />\n好似有得睇心理練好<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/社交恐懼症\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC%E7%97%87&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=11431408\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/社交恐懼症</a>"},{"pid":"223826e0ebda4c6ffd9828ae0ab758777bb4238c","tid":104912,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"我知你係醒目仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae465c3697b9421ec0a622b3e390d4da925af912","tid":104912,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三個字 三個字 咁講</blockquote><br />\n我試過，但唔知點解，到到果個moment ，就真係講唔到 <br />\n好似琴晚咁 ，落街買野食，個牌係咖哩吉列豬扒，我諗住叫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但果下我係feel到唔知點解會講唔到個咖哩呢兩隻字，我淨係講到吉列豬扒，塊臉好似唔受控制 ，之後我行過格離，拍拍自己塊臉 ，心諗應該ok既， <br />\n最後 我講左 吉列豬扒 然後再補多兩隻字 咖哩 ，。咁樣 ，<br />\n個老闆覺得好奇怪,  我咁樣講佢覺得我係要分開裝，我放棄解釋最後佢落左D沙律醬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果下好灰"},{"pid":"9a7298319c853c4c80acdc10a063e4bb4cb42f0f","tid":104912,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社交恐懼症？<br />\n會唔會覺得其他人注意你就好緊張？<br />\n好似有得睇心理練好<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/社交恐懼症\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC%E7%97%87&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=11431408\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/社交恐懼症</a></blockquote><br />\n應該係喇，因為好少社交，其實我中一果之前好活潑，之後就變到咁 ，"},{"pid":"6693d70931aeedd73e34b0431ec5d3b15aa096c5","tid":104912,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n補番小小資料，我阿媽都有口吃，佢已經定左， 我有可能係細過被阿媽影響到，但我冇話佢知，廢事佢傷心 <br />\n另外我平時性格 沈默是金，天蠍座，<br />\n但我係鐘意做D刺激野，比較外向D既活動，唔會收埋係屋企，主要係講野有問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c3d7d8dc3d39e16850e908e6b53d583a00dbc4","tid":104912,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"屌屌屌屌屌你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f00d4ab930189ea6a24b776199cf98ced9bcc86","tid":104912,"uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"多數係因為個腦快過把口<br />\n試下睇多d韓劇 slow down your brain a little bit"},{"pid":"8699bbefc9ef72169a5fb0096e1628116c66227b","tid":104912,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫人激嬲你 你聽到眼火爆果陣就屌鳩佢<br />\n最好鬧人果陣要夾雜啲粗口同英文<br />\n然後講野就會好流利</blockquote><br />\n 屌鳩人漏口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa2a06243e853353e7d8ddbd93246b33ad6db2b","tid":104912,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫人激嬲你 你聽到眼火爆果陣就屌鳩佢<br />\n最好鬧人果陣要夾雜啲粗口同英文<br />\n然後講野就會好流利</blockquote><br />\n 屌鳩人漏口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下講野諗到既野即講<br />\n唔好聽自己把聲"},{"pid":"cb7dde5c405153b9ae7f4f7b7713865b86174556","tid":104912,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"係咪一時講到啲字 一時講唔到"},{"pid":"0f5b92784b27dd4d31f925cf1e66e897639a15fd","tid":104912,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫人激嬲你 你聽到眼火爆果陣就屌鳩佢<br />\n最好鬧人果陣要夾雜啲粗口同英文<br />\n然後講野就會好流利</blockquote><br />\n 屌鳩人漏口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下講野諗到既野即講<br />\n唔好聽自己把聲</blockquote><br />\n同埋戒打丁"},{"pid":"f5e0fb460e78fa0c9e5704ec630d36c93d6b88cf","tid":104912,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪一時講到啲字 一時講唔到</blockquote><br />\n係，如果feel到講唔到我索性自我封閉一陣，然後再講"},{"pid":"e4b0822eee561be31a9f79d81c2ce11766207a90","tid":104912,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>叫人激嬲你 你聽到眼火爆果陣就屌鳩佢<br />\n最好鬧人果陣要夾雜啲粗口同英文<br />\n然後講野就會好流利</blockquote><br />\n 屌鳩人漏口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下講野諗到既野即講<br />\n唔好聽自己把聲</blockquote><br />\n同埋戒打丁</blockquote><br />\n我返宿舍學校，1-5冇得打 ，已經好健康"},{"pid":"5b61b8128acacee73411c9abb6a1be2b8ad9eea0","tid":104912,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:39:39.000Z","msg":"睇言語治癒師？"},{"pid":"0dbd806bfe412f6f2da4c6a1d8bdd185d624182a","tid":104912,"uid":35106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:39:57.000Z","msg":"細個幾嚴重 大個就少左<br />\n但有啲事都無講得唔夠快<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4ff295bb6730dd1ccb4c8bf4e8af2d122147b9","tid":104912,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"我初中時都有漏口問題，我諗主要係太心急，後來諗清楚先慢慢講就冇事；<br />\n但最近有時講野都會好似出唔到第一個音咁，要&quot;er&hellip; &quot;咁開左把聲先講到野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：25 歲"},{"pid":"33cd347abf2118651d5f85149591e9069276ec65","tid":104912,"uid":3179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"我都唔知自己算唔算...平時講廢話閒聊果陣就冇問題<br />\n但當我諗到好多意見同建議,個腦有好多野想表達果陣<br />\n就會開始口吃   個口好似跟唔切個腦啲反應咁<br />\n好想一次過表達哂所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcc212305fea93002718d4fe1c3c5c2efe45b1d","tid":104912,"uid":50112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:49:51.000Z","msg":"我都有 但我係間唔中先會發作 但次次發作都會比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發作個排有幾個字會令我好易口吃 eg 我、係、你、咁&hellip;<br />\n我習慣如果發作就會講野前吸一大口氣 咁就會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我阿媽都有啲口吃 唔知係咪遺傳&hellip;"},{"pid":"f4d771fafe27a990bd202c1138f5fde0aec42892","tid":104912,"uid":79502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我初中時都有漏口問題，我諗主要係太心急，後來諗清楚先慢慢講就冇事；<br />\n但最近有時講野都會好似出唔到第一個音咁，要&quot;er&hellip; &quot;咁開左把聲先講到野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：25 歲</blockquote><br />\n係呀，就係咁，有時講D音開頭就會之後都講到 ， 嚴重既就係講咩開頭都冇用 ，<br />\n例如 巴士號碼：72x， 麥當勞 ，<br />\n最煩就係麥當勞呢3隻字，次次同朋友講都放棄左，改做叫m記 ，"}]}